{"title":"Pearl iZUMi Celebrates MTB Origins with New Apparel Collection","link":"https://bikerumor.com/pearl-izumi-celebrates-mtb-origins-with-new-apparel-collection/","date":1696958289000,"content":"<p><img width=\"829\" height=\"313\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Shreddy-e1696886442912.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi Origins Collection Shreddy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Shreddy-e1696886442912.jpeg 829w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Shreddy-e1696886442912-297x112.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Shreddy-e1696886442912-800x302.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Shreddy-e1696886442912-120x45.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Shreddy-e1696886442912-768x290.jpeg 768w\" /></p>\n<p>The bicycle apparel and softgoods company, Pearl Izumi has <a href=\"https://www.pearlizumi.com/collections/origins-collection\">announced a new collection</a> that pays homage to the rebellious spirit of the first mountain bikers. The aptly named Origins Collection is available now and includes a tech t-shirt, mesh gloves, socks, pants, and a jacket.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mountain biking has always been a space that welcomed freedom of self-expression and creativity both on and off the bikes. Ditching the hard traditions and rules of the road bike scene, the early hippy-daredevil-godfathers of mountain biking embraced the counter-culture that they created. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pearl Izumi says that this collection “embodies the spirit of mountain biking’s free-thinking rebels of the ’70s and ’80s”.  Let’s take a look at the collection, shall we? </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Canyon Short Sleeve Jersey</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Short-Sleeve-Hero.jpeg\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Short-Sleeve-Hero.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi Origins Collection Canyon Short Sleeve Hero\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Short-Sleeve-Hero.jpeg 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Short-Sleeve-Hero-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Short-Sleeve-Hero-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Short-Sleeve-Hero-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Short-Sleeve-Hero-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Pearl Izumi</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=20053&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pearlizumi.com%2Fcollections%2Forigins-collection%2Fproducts%2Fmens-canyon-short-sleeve-jersey-19122202\">Canyon Jersey </a>looks like it would be perfect for a day of on-the-bike shreddy-ness mixed with some off-the-bike activities, like a fat burrito and a nice, cold adult beverage. Pearl Izumi says it fits like your “favorite t-shirt’ but gives you the “function of a technical jersey”. It’s made from highly breathable Drirelease fabric for all-day comfort, and raglan sleeves for on-bike mobility.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Jersy-front.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Jersy-front-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi Origins Collection Canyon Jersy front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Jersy-front-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Jersy-front-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Jersy-front-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Jersy-front-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Canyon-Jersy-front.jpeg 1000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-canyon-jersey-back.jpeg\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-canyon-jersey-back.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi Origins Collection canyon jersey back\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-canyon-jersey-back.jpeg 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-canyon-jersey-back-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-canyon-jersey-back-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-canyon-jersey-back-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-canyon-jersey-back-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features and Retail</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $45</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Color: Wild Orchid Origin</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sizes: S, M, L, Xl, XXL, and XXXL</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Pedal to Zero: Going by bike 16mi / 25km offsets the climate impact of this garment</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Constructed from 85% recycled polyester and 15% TENCEL™</li>\n\n\n\n<li>drirelease® fabric combines fast dry performance with a soft tee feel</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Dropped rear hem for on-bike coverage</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Raglan sleeves for great on-bike fit</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Relaxed fit</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Shipped rolled to reduce plastic packaging, wash to remove wrinkling</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Summit Pants</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-walking-e1696886025761.jpeg\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"940\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-walking-e1696886025761.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi Origins Collection Summit pants walking\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-walking-e1696886025761.jpeg 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-walking-e1696886025761-297x279.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-walking-e1696886025761-800x752.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-walking-e1696886025761-120x113.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-walking-e1696886025761-768x722.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Pearl Izumi knows that some rides call for extra protection from the elements and trail flora, that’s where the <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=20053&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pearlizumi.com%2Fcollections%2Forigins-collection%2Fproducts%2Fmens-summit-pants-19112201\">Summit Pants</a> enter the picture. This is a summer-weight pant that is said to be designed with mobility and pedaling performance in mind. It uses the same light and durable woven fabric as Pearl Izumi’s premium Summit Short, with a DWR coating to shed moisture. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-belt-buckle.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-belt-buckle-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi Origins Collection Summit pants belt buckle\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-belt-buckle-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-belt-buckle-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-belt-buckle-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-belt-buckle-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-pants-belt-buckle.jpeg 1000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-phone-pocket.jpeg\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-phone-pocket.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi Origins Collection Summit Pants phone pocket\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-phone-pocket.jpeg 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-phone-pocket-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-phone-pocket-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-phone-pocket-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-phone-pocket-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Summit Pants have perforated panels on the inside of the legs and dual Trail Access pockets to hold your essentials. Add a chamois liner and hit the trails.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants.jpeg\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi Origins Collection Summit Pants\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants.jpeg 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-back.jpeg\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-back.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi Origins Collection Summit Pants back\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-back.jpeg 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-back-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-back-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-back-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Pants-back-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features and Retail</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $145</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Colors: Black Origin and Phantom</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sizes: 28, 30, 32, 34, 36, and 38</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Pedal to Zero™: Going by bike 24mi / 38km offsets the climate impact of this garment</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Adjustable waist closure</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Durable water repellent (DWR) coating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Two zippered Trail Access side pockets shift contents to the back of the leg for pedaling comfort</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Compatible with most knee protection</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Standard fit33” inseam</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Shipped rolled to reduce plastic packaging, wash to remove wrinkling</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Summit Barrier Jacket</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-barrier-jacket-walking-e1696886149759.jpeg\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"946\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-barrier-jacket-walking-e1696886149759.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi Origins Collection Summit barrier jacket walking\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-barrier-jacket-walking-e1696886149759.jpeg 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-barrier-jacket-walking-e1696886149759-297x281.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-barrier-jacket-walking-e1696886149759-800x757.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-barrier-jacket-walking-e1696886149759-120x114.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-barrier-jacket-walking-e1696886149759-768x727.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=20053&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pearlizumi.com%2Fcollections%2Forigins-collection%2Fproducts%2Fmens-summit-barrier-jacket-19132210\">Summit Barrier Jacket</a> is an ultra-minimalist, ultra-packable jacket that will provide a little insurance against unpredictable weather. Pearl Izumi says the jacket packs down to the size of a baseball making it easy to carry with you on just about any ride. The lightweight material is windproof and has a PFC-free, DWR coating that sheds moisture, and it’s made from recycled materials.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Barrier-Jacket-with-hood.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Barrier-Jacket-with-hood-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi Origins Collection Summit Barrier Jacket with hood\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Barrier-Jacket-with-hood-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Barrier-Jacket-with-hood-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Barrier-Jacket-with-hood-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Barrier-Jacket-with-hood-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Barrier-Jacket-with-hood.jpeg 1000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Barrier-Jacket-back.jpeg\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Barrier-Jacket-back.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi Origins Collection Summit Barrier Jacket back\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-Izumi-Origins-Collection-Summit-Barrier-Jacket-back.jpeg 1000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Pearl-I